-- U.K. Mortgage Advances Rose 33% in May From April, CML Says
-- B y   J e n n i f e r   R y a n
-- 2012-07-12T08:33:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-12/u-k-mortgage-advances-rose-33-in-may-from-april-cml-says.html
U.K. mortgage advances rose 33
percent in May from the previous month, the  Council of Mortgage
Lenders  said today.  Banks advanced 48,300 loans for house purchase in May, up
24 percent from a year earlier, the CML said in an e-mailed
statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
